description: Gabather AB engages in the research and development of drug candidates for treatment of diseases affecting the central nervous system. The company is headquartered in Malmo, Skane. The company went IPO on 2014-11-03. The firm develops drug candidates for the treatment of several diseases originating in the central nervous system (CNS). The firm mainly focuses on anti-psychotics, anti-depressants and anxiolytics, analgesics, as well as conginition-enhancing treatments, including Alzheimer’s disease.
name: Gabather AB
